---
// 1Day体験セクション — プレミアムデザイン版
---

<section class="oneday-wrapper">
    <div class="oneday-container">
        <h2 class="oneday-title">Invitation</h2>
        <p class="oneday-description">
            本講座へのご参加をご検討中の方へ。<br>
            まずは一度、表参道のラボに流れる空気感と、<br>
            レッスンの全貌を体感いただく特別な一日をご用意しました。
        </p>
        <div class="oneday-pricing">
            <span class="oneday-label">Trial Lesson</span>
            <span class="oneday-price">¥13,000 <span class="oneday-tax">tax incl.</span></span>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="oneday-cta">
            Apply for 1-Day Experience
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
  .oneday-wrapper {
    padding: 12rem 2rem;
  }

  .oneday-container {
    max-width: 768px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
  }

  .oneday-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #B4934B;
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
  }

  .oneday-description {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 2.5;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #999;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
  }

  .oneday-pricing {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .oneday-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: #aaa;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: var(--f-sans);
  }

  .oneday-price {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 200;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #1C1C1A;
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
  }

  .oneday-tax {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #aaa;
  }

  .oneday-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid #D4AF37;
    padding: 1.25rem 4rem;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #1C1C1A;
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
    font-family: var(--f-sans);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .oneday-cta:hover {
    background-color: #D4AF37;
    color: white;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .oneday-wrapper {
      padding: 6rem 1rem;
    }

    .oneday-container {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .oneday-title {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .oneday-cta {
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      font-size: 9px;
    }
  }
</style>
